<h2 class="text--sanserif u-text--31">How Do People Around the Globe Evaluate Their Lives?</h2>
<p class="u-text--16 card--margin-btm0">Gallup has been measuring how people evaluate their lives in the U.S. and around the globe for more than a decade through the Life Evaluation Index. Learn more about how that measure is useful in understanding people&#39;s lives.</p>
